devdoc.details: A simple contract to simulate a vending machine that sells "Digital Sodas".

buySoda().details: Allows anyone to buy a soda by sending exactly 0.01 ETH.

getBalance().details: Allows the owner to see the current Ether balance of the machine.

restock(uint256).details: Allows the owner to restock the machine.

params._amount: The number of sodas to add to the inventory.

withdrawProfits().details: Allows the owner to withdraw all collected profits.
